Frequency of Comments

The activity of users on the discussion boards is quite variable, with user “Cuboctahedron” racking up 1063 comments over all the boards and 37% of users only made one comment.

The total number of interactions between all users is 5987, removing those users who only commented once decreases this to 5987 interactions.
